      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHARGE THE CARD (2) was in the minors two back (18.82) at Dubbo but ran below best last time there, finishing 7th. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Can bounce back. LUMEAH MONTE (6) doesn't win out of turn. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (20.28) at this track. Hard to beat again. MARVIN MONELLI (5) comes off an average effort last start when fifth at this track over 340m behind Eva Cargo (20.27) in a Grade 5. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Should play a prominent role. KIANDO ESTATE (1) raced handy last time and scored. Sure to run well again.",
